data.description: Beautifully updated 3 bed & 1 bath home with great curb appeal. The home features a backyard perfect for relaxing with an above ground pool and covered back patio area!  Home offers an open concept with updates throughout including upgrades such as double pane windows (2021) and a new roof (August 2022). Tile (hallway) and flooring throughout the home updated in the last 5 years. Enjoy your evening by the pool, on the covered patio, or stop by the nearby park! Perfect for first time homebuyers or would make for a great investment​​‌​​​​‌​‌​​​‌​​​​‌‌​​​​​​‌‌​​​​ property!
